snippet.title: The Legend of Zelda 35th Anniversary Game & Watch - Announcement Trailer | E3 2021
snippet.description:
To commemorate 35 years of The Legends of Zelda, Nintendo is releasing a Game and Watch handheld containing several classic Zelda games.

#IGN #E32021 #SummerofGaming
